ygData.messageBody:
Kitasi of E'ci 15th level wood elf dedicated to Erollisi
Marr
Solo often, party when I can find
likeminded rp'ers
fav blue to kill: Hmmm, Good question, no idea really
Unfav death place: No question, the Gorge, usually while some
evil eyes pet
Most deaths getting corpse: Pretty boring here, one, after that I always
weave Purifying Rythyms and Selo's
in the Gorge!
Most level with no death: Five, or does it only count as four since
the first death dropped me
back a level?
Definitely Weaving
Bio screen under construction, but
centers around Kithicor now instead
of my hunt for Crookstinger, who only
2 days after buying his dagger, I ran into and slew
and got another one!

Kitasi, looking for his Watson

Welcome~

Good to meet you - we all wanna know:
what level you are;
do you party or solo;
fav blue to kill;
unfav place to die in;
most number of deaths getting a corpse back;
most number of levels with no death (if any :);

please also submit a suggestion for the term to describe playing two songs
at once (don't say 'twisting' <g>); run out and buy a Dragoon Dirk; and tell
us what in your 'bio' screen when ppl inspect your equipment. There now you
are up date <bg>!!

Seriously, Welcome!

Sylly
Bard of the 15th level
a.k.a. Robo-Bard
camped out somewhere on Innoruuk
